Description: Provides an end-to-end pipeline for stock-market data
    workflows in pure R. Index constituents are scraped from
    'Wikipedia' and OHLCV history is pulled from 'Yahoo Finance'.
    Analysis utilities cover NA cleaning, time-series format conversion
    via 'tsbox', period aggregation with an OHLCV-aware mode, exploratory
    data analysis (line plots, ACF / PACF, STL decomposition) and
    ARIMA-based forecasting with multi-level confidence bands.
